    <summary>Bizrate Buyers Survey &amp; Medal Code.</summary>
    <description>This module will add the Bizrate callback and Survey code to the success page on your Magento store. It also allows you to add the Bizrate Medal code to the Footer, Left sidebar or Right sidebar. It has the option of allowing you to choose the small or regular sized Bizrate Medal. There are also advanced options for selecting the Product attribute that represents the GTIN field for your products as well as direct editing of the HTML for the Bizrate Medal code.</description>
    <notes>- updated code so for configurable products it will send the main product's URL and SKU&#xD;
- updated code so the order's item details (for bizrate) are not loaded by SKU (since sku can change under specific circumstances) but by the product ID.&#xD;
</notes>
